N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 2.2 - Pending proceedings

State Regulations

This Chapter and regulations made by the commissioner
pursuant thereto (see Chapter II of this Title) shall not affect any proceeding
pending before the Regents or the commissioner, or both, on October 29, 1954, and such proceedings shall continue under and be controlled by the rules of the

Regents and of the commissioner in effect prior to such date. Notes
